OL,6,FLocal elections will take place across
OL,7,FEngland and Wales on Thursday 2 May,
OL,8,Fwith some important choices for voters
OL,9,Fin Yorkshire and Lincolnshire.
OL,11,FHere is a round-up of all of the
OL,12,Felections taking place.
