OL,3,CAll you need to know about local
OL,4,Celections in Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,6,FLike the new York and North Yorkshire
OL,7,Fmayor, the mayor of West Yorkshire has
OL,8,Fpowers over transport, skills and the
OL,9,Fpolice and fire services.
OL,11,FIn South Yorkshire, those powers -
OL,12,Fformerly held by the police, fire and
OL,13,Fcrime commissioner - are being added
OL,14,Fto the mayor's responsibilities. The
OL,15,Fchange means the current mayor,
OL,16,FLabour's Oliver Coppard, will face an
OL,17,Felection just two years into what
OL,18,Fshould have been a four-year term.
