OL,6,FPCC are elected to hold the police to
OL,7,Faccount. They have responsibility for
OL,8,Ftheir police force's finances and can
OL,9,Fappoint or dismiss the chief
OL,10,Fconstable. Once elected, each PCC must
OL,11,Fproduce a police and crime plan, which
OL,12,Fsets their force's strategic direction.
